                    type === TransactionType.SALE ? 'bg-emerald-600 shadow-emerald-50 hover:bg-emerald-700' : 'bg-red-600 shadow-red-50 hover:bg-red-700'
                  }`}
                >
                  Save Entry
                </button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
};

